    "chatPageUserDebouncePrompt": "帮我写一个 React 自定义 Hook，用来做防抖搜索。",
    "chatPageAssistantDebounceReply": "好的，这是一个 `useDebounceSearch` Hook 的实现：\n\n```typescript\nfunction useDebounceSearch(delay = 300) {\n  const [query, setQuery] = useState('')\n  const [debouncedQuery, setDebouncedQuery] = useState('')\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n      setDebouncedQuery(query)\n    }, delay)\n    return () => clearTimeout(timer)\n  }, [query, delay])\n\n  return { query, setQuery, debouncedQuery }\n}\n```\n\n**主要特点：**\n1. 输入变化后延迟 300ms 才触发实际搜索\n2. 每次输入都会重置计时器，避免频繁请求\n3. 组件卸载时自动清理 timer",
    "chatPageAssistantDebounceThinking1": "分析用户需求：React 防抖搜索 Hook",
    "chatPageAssistantDebounceThinking2": "选择 `useState` + `useEffect` 作为基础实现",
    "chatPageAssistantDebounceThinking3": "添加清理逻辑避免定时器泄漏",
    "chatPageUserLoadingPrompt": "能加上 loading 状态和取消请求的功能吗？",
    "chatPageAssistantLoadingReply": "当然可以！这里是增强版本，加入了 `loading` 状态和 `AbortController` 取消请求：\n\n```typescript\nfunction useDebounceSearch<T>(fetcher: (q: string, signal: AbortSignal) => Promise<T>, delay = 300) {\n  const [query, setQuery] = useState('')\n  const [data, setData] = useState<T | null>(null)\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false)\n  const abortRef = useRef<AbortController>()\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (!query) { setData(null); return }\n    const timer = setTimeout(async () => {\n      abortRef.current?.abort()\n      const ctrl = new AbortController()\n      abortRef.current = ctrl\n      setLoading(true)\n      try {\n        const res = await fetcher(query, ctrl.signal)\n        if (!ctrl.signal.aborted) setData(res)\n      } finally {\n        if (!ctrl.signal.aborted) setLoading(false)\n      }\n    }, delay)\n    return () => clearTimeout(timer)\n  }, [query, delay, fetcher])\n\n  return { query, setQuery, data, loading }\n}\n```\n\n**改进点：**\n- 🔄 `loading` 状态跟踪请求进度\n- ❌ 新请求发起前自动取消上一个未完成的请求\n- 🛡️ 使用 `AbortSignal` 防止竞态条件",
    "chatPageAssistantLoadingThinking1": "评估需求：loading 状态 + 取消请求",
    "chatPageAssistantLoadingThinking2": "引入 `AbortController` 管理请求生命周期",
    "chatPageAssistantLoadingThinking3": "避免旧请求结果覆盖新结果",
    "chatPageAssistantLoadingThinking4": "保留泛型能力以提升复用性",
